Jeremy Corbyn will debut in the session of questions to the Prime Minister
After the election of Mr. Corbyn, his debut at the question session is expected to the Prime Minister with great impatience
Labour’s new leader Jeremy Corbyn will speak to the Prime Minister for the first time at a session of questions, for the first time battling with David Cameron.
