Of course, it depends on how good a baker you are.
Badly glued lumps of flour, sugar and fat will rather make people pretend to be asleep when you knock on them.
Theft of food is a typical crime in student dormitories.
Of course, embezzling someone's chicken is stealing, but is it stealing to take a little milk for tea?
